---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - Domain Discoverer" description="We respect your privacy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect information, and how to contact us.">
  <section class="container-pad">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We take privacy seriously. This policy explains what we collect, how we use it, and your choices. If you have questions, please contact us.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-8 mb-2">What This Site Does</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">DomainDiscoverer.com helps visitors discover valuable domain names. Visitors can check domain availability and explore a curated list of tools that support research.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-white/80 max-w-3xl space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Email address</strong> if you subscribe to our newsletter via the footer form powered by Netlify Forms.</li>
      <li><strong>Basic logs</strong> that Netlify may provide for security and performance.</li>
      <li><strong>Function requests</strong> such as domain availability checks. We do not store the domain queries you enter.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-white/80 max-w-3xl space-y-1">
      <li>To send the newsletter you requested</li>
      <li>To maintain and improve site reliability</li>
      <li>To respond when you contact us</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Email and Unsubscribe</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We only email people who opt in. Every message includes an unsubscribe link or clear directions to opt out. You can also contact us to be removed.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We use functional cookies to keep the site running. You can manage cookies in your browser. Our banner gives a simple control for consent.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Third Party Links</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We link to third party tools and registrars. Their policies apply when you use those services. We recommend that you read them before you proceed.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Security</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We use modern hosting and follow sensible practices to protect data. No method is perfect, so please contact us if you find any issue.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Your Choices</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-white/80 max-w-3xl space-y-1">
      <li>Unsubscribe from emails at any time</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your newsletter address</li>
      <li>Control cookies in your browser</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">For privacy requests, use our <a class="underline" href="/contact">contact page</a>. We respond as quickly as possible.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

